# Minimal composite asset for Phase C0b/D/C verification.
# A 3x1x3 wooden base with a 3x0x3 single-layer lid hinged at the back edge.
#
# The lid is a single horizontal layer of cubes (y=1) tagged with the movable
# part "lid". The hinge keyword `back_top` resolves to the +Z, +Y corner of the
# lid's AABB so the lid rotates open backwards like a treasure chest.
# part: base
C 0 0 0 Wood
C 1 0 0 Wood
C 2 0 0 Wood
C 0 0 1 Wood
C 1 0 1 Wood
C 2 0 1 Wood
C 0 0 2 Wood
C 1 0 2 Wood
C 2 0 2 Wood
# part: lid hinge=back_top axis=x
C 0 1 0 Wood
C 1 1 0 Wood
C 2 1 0 Wood
C 0 1 1 Wood
C 1 1 1 Wood
C 2 1 1 Wood
C 0 1 2 Wood
C 1 1 2 Wood
C 2 1 2 Wood
